{"tid":49061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）笑到仆街 肥閪過敏","createTime":"2016-12-21T12:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T16:54:25.000Z","uid":45270,"like":153,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b0478929f59db2bb04bd97e35b41a61abfdeab","tid":49061,"uid":45270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z84e768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz84e768.jpg&h=871cbc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條肥豬閪 廿鳩幾歲人叫自己做玲子<br />\n仲好撚鍾意玩偶像閃卡 (用QR code掃上網幫公仔換衫 自己整偶像 我補習細路都好鍾意玩）<br />\n<br />\n跟住啦 而家話啲閃卡有粉 導致過敏 跟著話佢隻手腫撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點黎啦 佢隻手肥過豬蹄 點撚樣睇到腫左？屌 肥過閪 你話你隻手生lin都仲得啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9674GRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9674GRB.jpg&h=44da6a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =主持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：豬閪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：姐係本身（你隻手）唔係咁（撚肥）嘅？<br />\n我真係 唧一聲 笑撚左<br />\n<br />\n跟著跟著 <br />\n佢冇啦啦喊 話咩佢好耐都冇掂過佢bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著我同主持都倒抽一口氣 bb..究竟係乜撚野暗號黎嘅呢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟著個主持唯有搏一搏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你⋯你bb幾大呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：八個月大啦⋯佢而家嬲左我 唔俾我掂佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我估唔到玩下卡都影響到我屋企人 影響到我工作<br />\n<br />\n屌 個問答就係呢度完左⋯希望個主持最後冇俾個肥閪食撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b5740aa6de1fc3382f5c6c6f0e5bf9d07a15ab","tid":49061,"uid":41643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e6a99f888b54bd6e74a66c06b5a72675bc64e1","tid":49061,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769a36d93227841a651560a88af44cc9fd81bce0","tid":49061,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"6a72ef73b15c753821afff964b896adecff5f307","tid":49061,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"236925c1f33ca117f7e4a911f80f3abf56e9ad33","tid":49061,"uid":37618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到打撚曬冷陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc2bb82a4370d3fa323f480bcf71dbca146b121","tid":49061,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:58:05.000Z","msg":"八個月大啦⋯佢而家嬲左我 唔俾我掂佢啦<br />\n呢句好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f207c42b0a9734787723de3b2edab450b5be7cd6","tid":49061,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"我中學個時都有個死肥婆<br />\n好鍾意幫自己改日本名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=